5|$|The {{doctrine}} of the Pentecostal Holiness Church is articulated in the Apostles' Creed and the Articles of Faith. The Articles were placed in their present form in 1945. The first four articles are {{essentially the same as}} the first four Articles of Religion of <b>the</b> <b>Methodist</b> Church.|$|E
